HERE IS THE DETAILS OF MOVIE'S SOUNDTRACK: 

Neal 'n' NikkiSoundtrack album by Salim–SulaimanReleased2 November 2005GenreFeature film soundtrackLabelYRF Music
The music was composed by Salim–Sulaiman.
"Neal 'n' Nikki", "Halla Re", "I'm In Love", "Ankh Ladiye", "I Just Wanna Spend My Life With You", and "Neal 'n' Nikki" (The Naughty Mix) all have lyrics written by Anvita Dutt Guptan.
"Neal 'n' Nikki", and "Neal 'n' Nikki" (The Naughty Mix) both feature KK as a singer.
"Neal 'n' Nikki", "Halla Re", "I'm In Love", and "Ankh Ladiye" all feature Shweta Pandit as a singer.
"I'm In Love" features Sonu Nigam as a singer.
"I Just Wanna Spend My Life With You", and "Neal 'n' Nikki" (The Naughty Mix) both feature Clinton Cerejo as a singer.
"I Just Wanna Spend My Life With You", and "Neal 'n' Nikki" (The Naughty Mix) both feature Dominique Cerejo as a singer.
"I'm In Love" features Mahalakshmi Iyer as a singer.
